@@aPALADIN@@W

Paladins are oathbound vanguards who turn faith into forward pressure. Their
style is direct: close distance, hold formation, and punish evil with sanctified
steel.

@@aPassive class advantages@@W
  * @@wExtra attack round@@W while Paladin remort is active.
  * @@wPhysical damage@@W bonus from Paladin levels
    (+0.4% per level, up to +40% at 100).
  * @@wHealing throughput@@W bonus
    (+1.5% per level, up to +150% at 100).

@@aUnique Paladin mechanics@@W
  * Access to @@wPaladin stance@@W (melee + survivability + healing posture).
  * Hybrid holy/melee kit with strong support crossover into Templar path.
  * Uses @@wWisdom@@W as prime remort attribute.

@@aPaladin reincarnation bonuses@@W
  * @@wPaladin + Priest remort reincarnations >= 20@@W unlocks:
    @@wTwo-Handed@@W, @@wEquip Buckler@@W, and @@wEquip Wand@@W permanently.

See also: @@mremort stance priest templar reincarnate@@W
